**Special Containment Procedures:** SCP-8651-A instances are to send direct messages to D-14's[[footnote]]D-14 is currently contained in a sound-proof chamber located in Site-01.[[/footnote]] e-mail address when attempting to remove SCP-8651's effect.[[footnote]]Personnel are to follow the instructions stated at the bottommost of this file.[[/footnote]] Personnel are also to ignore all direct messages containing audio files before having them properly inspected by O5-2. 
@@@@
