SCP-8651-A instances will initially perceive low-frequency auditory stimuli as the contents of SCP-8651. This effect will progressively intensify, ultimately leading to all auditory input being perceived as an extremely loud instance of SCP-8651, resulting in extreme pain in the instance's auditory sensory organs.

@@@@
