----
Seven,

I seem to have come across the most elegant, astonishing, and beautiful piece of audio I have ever heard. It is difficult to articulate how much emotion can be conveyed in so brief a recording, yet this file manages it effortlessly.

There is a certain rawness to it—something immediate and unfiltered—that I find quite compelling. I have replayed it several times now, and each instance has only reinforced my initial impression.

I have attached it below. I would strongly encourage you to listen at your earliest convenience. I believe you will find it… memorable. I would be very interested to hear your thoughts afterward.

Regards, O5-2
[[include :scp-wiki:component:audio-player-woed-source
